headline: Q3 Consumer Subscription Earnings: Duolingo (NASDAQ:DUOL) Earns Top Marks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Duolingo (NASDAQ:DUOL) and the rest of the consumer subscription stocks fared in Q3.
